          "guid": "mrxyaioflyr8tp36",
          "message": {
            "text": "The render-count pin is 4, not 3: arraySignal mutations re-run the mount render by design (that render is how the patch queue drains), so initial + two banner toggles + the granular remove = 4. The invariant this test asserts is that the four SELECTION flips add zero renders — they flow entirely through the per-row binding effects. If this pin breaks with a higher count, a selection flip started re-rendering (the FC-B3 regression); if lower, the patch-drain model changed.",
            "markdown": "The render-count pin is 4, not 3: arraySignal mutations re-run the mount render by design (that render is how the patch queue drains), so initial + two banner toggles + the granular remove = 4. The invariant this test asserts is that the four SELECTION flips add zero renders — they flow entirely through the per-row binding effects. If this pin breaks with a higher count, a selection flip started re-rendering (the FC-B3 regression); if lower, the patch-drain model changed."
          },
          "locations": [
            {
              "physicalLocation": {
                "artifactLocation": {
                  "uri": "tests/unit/kf380-interaction-matrix.test.tsx"
                },
                "region": {
                  "startLine": 372,
                  "endLine": 374,
                  "snippet": {
                    "text": "    // Selection flips never re-ran the render: only the initial render, the\n    // two banner toggles, and the granular remove (patch drain) did.\n    expect(render).toHaveBeenCalledTimes(4);"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          ],
